About Game:
************
New adventures in Gizmo Land! Again civilians of Gizmo Land are threatened with danger! An attempt to celebrate Halloween ended with an enormous number of ghosts. It's not for the first time when John, Sid and Kurt need to think carefully about the remedy of situation.

New riddles, an interesting plotline, excellent music and brave Gizmos are waiting for you!

Game Features:
**************
Exciting nonogram puzzles up to 30 x 30 grids!
Breathtaking Halloween adventures in Gizmo Land!
Dozens of hours of relaxing gameplay!
Gorgeous steampunk music and sound effects

